name: Spider Ladybug Stickman Swing
description:
It’s time to play the best Game of Stickman, Challenge yourself to execute all these swing and hook tricks in a row like a boss.

Tap and hold to hook swing and make incredible jumps; Avoid every obstacle that stands in your way.

In this game, embody the Spider Ladybug Stickman Swing
Finish all the levels with the same agility as a spider.
